\c 21
\s UJesu ungena eJerusalema
\p
\v 1 Kwathi-ke sebesondele eJerusalema\x + Mark. 11.1-10. Luka 19.29-38.\x*, sebefikile eBetfage\x + Mark. 11.1. Luka 19.29.\x* entabeni yeMihlwathi\x + 24.3; 26.30. Joha. 8.1. Seb. 1.12. Zek. 14.4.\x*, khona uJesu wathuma abafundi ababili,
\v 2 esithi kubo: Hambani liye emzaneni okhangelene lani, lizahle libone ubabhemi ekhulekiwe, lethole lilaye; li\add ba\add*khulule, li\add ba\add*lethe kimi.
\v 3 Futhi uba umuntu ekhuluma ulutho kini, lizakuthi: INkosi iyabaswela; njalo uzahle abathumele.
\v 4 Njalo konke lokhu kwenzeka, ukuze kugcwaliseke okwakhulunywa ngumprofethi\x + Joha. 12.12-15.\x*, ukuthi:
\v 5 Tshelani indodakazi yeSiyoni \add ukuthi\x + Isa. 62.11.\x*\add*: Khangela, iNkosi yakho iyeza kuwe, imnene igade ubabhemi, lethole inkonyana yenyamazana yokuthwala\x + Zek. 9.9.\x*.
\v 6 Abafundi bahamba-ke, benza njengalokhu uJesu wayebalayile,
\v 7 baletha ubabhemi lethole, babeka izembatho zabo phezu kwabo, ba\add m\add*hlalisa phezu kwazo\x + Mark. 11.7. Luka 19.35.\x*.
\v 8 Lenengi lexuku lendlala ezalo izembatho endleleni\x + 2 Kho. 9.13.\x*; labanye bagamula ingatsha zezihlahla, ba\add z\add*endlala endleleni\x + Levi 23.40.\x*.
\v 9 Lamaxuku ayehamba phambili lababelandela bamemeza, besithi: \w Hosana\w** kuyo iNdodana kaDavida\x + 21.15. Hlab. 118.25.\x*! Ubusisiwe ozayo ebizweni leNkosi\x + Hlab. 118.26. Luka 13.35.\x*. Hosana\x + 21.15. Hlab. 118.25.\x* kweliphezulu\x + Luka 2.14. Jobe 16.19.\x*!
\p
\v 10 Esengenile eJerusalema\x + Mark. 11.15.\x* umuzi wonke wanyakazela usithi: Ngubani lo\x + Ruthe 1.19.\x*?
\v 11 Amaxuku asesithi: Lo nguJesu umprofethi\x + 21.46. Luka 7.16. Joha. 6.14.\x*, oweNazaretha yeGalili\x + 2.23.\x*.
\s Ukuhlanjululwa kwethempeli
\p
\v 12 UJesu wasengena ethempelini likaNkulunkulu, wabaxotsha bonke ababethengisa lababethenga ethempelini\x + Mark. 11.15-19. Luka 19.45-47. Mal. 3.1-3. Joha. 2.13-17.\x*, wasegenqula amatafula\x + 25.27. Luka 19.23. Seb. 6.2.\x* ababentshintshelana imali\x + Dute. 14.25.\x*, lezihlalo zalabo ababethengisa amajuba\x + Levi 1.14.\x*.
\v 13 Wasesithi kubo: Kulotshiwe \add ukuthi\add*: Indlu yami izabizwa ngokuthi yindlu yomkhuleko\x + Isa. 56.7.\x*; kodwa lina liyenze ubhalu\x + Jer. 7.11.\x* lwabaphangi\x + 26.55.\x*.
\v 14 Kwasekufika kuye iziphofu leziqhuli ethempelini; wasezisilisa.
\v 15 Kodwa abapristi abakhulu lababhali sebebonile izimangaliso azenzayo, labantwana bememeza ethempelini, besithi: Hosana eNdodaneni kaDavida\x + 21.9.\x*! bathukuthela,
\v 16 basebesithi kuye: Uyakuzwa lokhu yini abakutshoyo laba? UJesu wasesithi kubo: Yebo; alikaze lifunde yini ukuthi: Emlonyeni\x + Hlab. 8.2.\x* wezingane lowabamunyayo\x + 11.25.\x* uphelelise indumiso\x + Roma 9.22. Heb. 10.5.\x*?
\v 17 Wasebatshiya waphuma phandle komuzi esiya eBethani, walala khona\x + 26.6. Mark. 11.1,11,12; 14.3. Luka 19.29; 24.50. Joha. 11.1,18; 12.1.\x*.
\s Ukuthukwa komkhiwa
\p
\v 18 Kwathi ebuyela emzini ekuseni, walamba\x + 21.18,19, Mark. 11.12-14.\x*;
\v 19 kwathi ebona umkhiwa othile endleleni, wasondela kuwo, kodwa katholanga lutho kuwo ngaphandle kwamahlamvu wodwa; wathi kuwo: Kakungabe kusavela isithelo kuwe lanini. Njalo umkhiwa wahle wabuna.
\v 20 Kwathi bebona \add lokhu\add* abafundi bakhe bamangala, besithi: Umkhiwa uhle wabuna njani\x + Mark. 11.20-24.\x*?
\v 21 UJesu wasephendula wathi kubo: Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Uba lilokholo\x + 17.20.\x*, lingathandabuzi, kaliyikwenza lokhu okomkhiwa kuphela\x + Mark. 11.23. Seb. 10.20; 11.12. Roma 4.20; 14.23. Jak. 1.6; 2.4.\x*, kodwa loba lisithi lakulintaba: Qutshunwa uphoselwe olwandle, kuzakwenzeka\x + 21.1.\x*.
\v 22 Njalo konke loba kuyini elikucelayo emkhulekweni, likholwa, lizakwemukela\x + 7.7. Jak. 5.16.\x*.
\s Igunya likaJesu
\p
\v 23 Kwathi esengenile ethempelini, abapristi abakhulu labadala babantu basondela kuye esafundisa\x + Mark. 11.27-33. Luka 20.1-8.\x*, bathi: Izinto lezi uzenza ngaliphi igunya? Njalo ngubani okunike leligunya\x + Eks. 2.14. Seb. 4.7; 7.27.\x*?
\v 24 UJesu wasephendula wathi kubo: Lami ngizalibuza umbuzo ube munye; uba lingitshela lokhu, lami ngizalitshela ukuthi ngenza lezizinto ngaliphi igunya:
\v 25 Ubhabhathizo lukaJohane lwavela ngaphi? Ezulwini kumbe ebantwini? Basebekhulumisana, besithi: Uba sisithi: Ezulwini, uzakuthi kithi: Pho kalikholwanga kuye ngani\x + Luka 3.15.\x*?
\v 26 Kodwa uba sisithi: Ebantwini, siyesaba ixuku\x + 14.5. 21.46.\x*; ngoba bonke bamphatha uJohane njengomprofethi\x + 11.9.\x*.
\v 27 Basebemphendula uJesu bathi: Kasazi. Wasesithi kubo: Lami kangilitsheli ukuthi ngenza lezizinto ngaliphi igunya.
\s Umfanekiso wamadodana amabili
\p
\v 28 Kanti licabangani\x + 18.12.\x*? Umuntu wayelamadodana amabili; waya kweyokuqala wathi: Mntana\add mi\add*, hamba, uyesebenza lamuhla esivinini sami\x + 21.33. 20.1.\x*.
\v 29 Kodwa yaphendula yathi: Angifuni. Kodwa emva kwalokho yaphenduka, yahamba\x + 21.32.27.3. 2 Kor. 7.8. Heb. 7.21.\x*.
\v 30 Wasesiya kweyesibili watsho ngokunjalo. Yona-ke yaphendula yathi: Ngiya\add hamba\add*, nkosi. Kodwa kayiyanga.
\v 31 Yiyiphi kulawo amabili eyenza intando kayise? Bathi kuye: Eyokuqala. UJesu wathi kubo: Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Abathelisi\x + 18.17.\x* lezifebe bayangena embusweni kaNkulunkulu phambi kwenu\x + Luka 7.37-50.\x*.
\v 32 Ngoba uJohane wafika kini ngendlela yokulunga, kalikholwanga kuye\x + 3.1,8-12.19.20.\x*; kodwa abathelisi lezifebe\x + Luka 3.12,13; 7.29.\x* bakholwa kuye\x + Luka 3.12,13; 7.29.\x*; kodwa lina seli\add ku\add*bonile kaliphendukanga emva kwalokho ukuthi likholwe kuye\x + 21.33. 20.1.\x*.
\s Umfanekiso wabalimi besivini
\p
\v 33 Zwanini omunye umfanekiso. Kwakukhona umuntu othile ongumninimuzi\x + Mark. 12.1-12. Luka 20.9-19.\x*, owahlanyela isivini\x + Hlab. 80.8.\x*, wasibiyela ngothango\x + Isa. 5.2.\x*, wagebha isikhamelo\x + Isa. 5.2.\x* kuso, wakha umphotshongo\x + Isa. 5.2.\x*, wasiqhatshisa kubalimi, waya kwelinye ilizwe\x + 25.14,15. Luka 15.13.\x*.
\v 34 Kwathi sekusondele isikhathi sezithelo, wathuma inceku zakhe kubalimi, ukuze zemukele izithelo zakhe.
\v 35 Abalimi basebezibamba inceku zakhe, enye bayitshaya\x + 5.12. Heb. 11.36,37. 2 Lan. 36.16. Seb. 5.40. 2 Kor. 11.24,25.\x*, lenye bayibulala\x + 22.6; 23.34,37. 1 Thes. 2.15. Heb. 11.37. Jer. 26.23. Neh. 9.26.\x*, lenye bayikhanda ngamatshe\x + 23.37. 2 Lan. 24.21. Heb. 11.37.\x*.
\v 36 Wabuya wathuma ezinye inceku ezinengi kulezokuqala\x + 22.4.\x*; basebesenza njalo kulezo.
\v 37 Ekucineni wasethuma indodana yakhe kubo, esithi: Bazayihlonipha indodana yami\x + Heb. 12.9.\x*.
\v 38 Kodwa abalimi sebeyibonile indodana bakhulumisana \add besithi\add*: Le yindlalifa\x + Heb. 1.2.\x*; wozani, siyibulale, njalo sibambe ilifa layo\x + 26.3; 27.1. Joha. 11.53. Seb. 4.27. 2 Sam. 14.7.\x*.
\v 39 Basebeyibamba\x + 26.50. 27.50. Seb. 2.23; 5.30.\x* ba\add yi\add*phosela ngaphandle kwesivini, ba\add yi\add*bulala\x + Heb. 13.12.\x*.
\v 40 Ngakho mhla kufika umninisivini, uzabenzani abalimi labo?
\v 41 Bathi kuye: Uzababhubhisa kakubi labo ababi\x + Luka 21.24.\x*, njalo uzaqhatshisa isivini kwabanye abalimi, abazamnika izithelo ngezikhathi zazo\x + Seb. 13.46; 18.6; 28.28.\x*.
\p
\v 42 UJesu wathi kubo: Alikaze lifunde yini emibhalweni \add ukuthi\add*: Ilitshe abakhi abalalayo, yilo eseliyinhloko yengonsi; lokhu yikwenza kweNkosi; njalo kuyamangalisa emehlweni ethu\x + Hlab. 118.22,23. Seb. 4.11. Isa. 28.16. Efe. 2.20. 1 Pet. 2.6.\x*?
\v 43 Ngakho ngithi kini: Lizakwemukwa umbuso kaNkulunkulu, unikwe isizwe esithela izithelo zawo\x + 8.12. Luka 14.24.\x*.
\v 44 Lalowo owela phezu kwalelilitshe uzaphahlazwa\x + Isa. 8.14,15. Zek. 12.3. Luka 20.18. Roma 9.33. 1 Pet. 2.7,8. Luka 2.34.\x*; kodwa loba ngubani eliwela phezu kwakhe lizamchoboza\x + Dan. 2.34,35,44. Isa.60.12.\x*.
\p
\v 45 Kwathi abapristi abakhulu labaFarisi sebezwile imifanekiso yakhe bazi ukuthi ubekhuluma ngabo.
\v 46 Kwathi sebedinga ukumbamba\x + 21.15. Mark. 11.18. Luka 19.47. Joha. 7.25,30,44.\x* besaba amaxuku\x + 21.26.\x*, ngoba ayemphatha njengomprofethi\x + 21.11.\x*.